spec_data.Name: kabi-yum-plugins
spec_data.Description:
The kABI yum plugins package contains a yum plugin that can be used in order
to enforce that only those third party kernel module packages meeting CentOS
kernel ABI requirements are installed. The plugin requires that those drivers
be packaged in accordance with CentOS Driver Update Program guidelines.
